Achievements.Name: First Glory
Achievements.Description: Awarded for your first win.

Achievements.Name: Perfect 10
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning 10 consecutive matches.

Achievements.Name: Come Back Win
Achievements.Description: Awarded for your first Come Back Win.

Achievements.Name: Last Gasp Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for scoring the Winner in Extra Time.

Achievements.Name: World Traveller
Achievements.Description: A Title awarded for playing at all featured Stadiums. (Excludes ones created in Edit Mode.)

Achievements.Name: The Gentleman
Achievements.Description: Awarded for committing less than 1 Foul per match on average in your last 10 Matches.

Achievements.Name: Possession Play
Achievements.Description: Awarded for having a Possession Rate of 60% or higher in your last 10 Matches.

Achievements.Name: Hat-trick Hero
Achievements.Description: Awarded for scoring 5 hat-tricks.

Achievements.Name: Predatory Striker
Achievements.Description: Awarded for playing over 20 Matches, averaging 2 plus goals per Match in your last 10.

Achievements.Name: Dead-ball Expert
Achievements.Description: Awarded for scoring 5 Direct Free-Kicks.

Achievements.Name: Long Ranger
Achievements.Description: Awarded for scoring from 35m out or more.

Achievements.Name: League Winner
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning one of the top leagues in [Master League]

Achievements.Name: European Elite 16
Achievements.Description: Awarded for making the Knockout phase of the UEFA Champions League in [Master League] .

Achievements.Name: Kings of Europe
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning the Master League UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: The Invincibles
Achievements.Description: Awarded for an undefeated season in Master League winning League, Cup and UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: No.1 Club
Achievements.Description: Awarded for topping the Team Ranking in Master League.

Achievements.Name: World Footballer of the Year
Achievements.Description: Awarded if a member of your team wins World Footballer of the Year in Master League.

Achievements.Name: 10 years of Service
Achievements.Description: An award to honour 10 years of service in Master League.

Achievements.Name: The Debutant
Achievements.Description: Awarded for your First Professional Appearance in Become a Legend.

Achievements.Name: International Cup Debut
Achievements.Description: Awarded for your First Appearance in the Become a Legend International Cup.

Achievements.Name: International Cup MVP
Achievements.Description: Awarded for being named International Cup Player of the Tournament in Become a Legend.

Achievements.Name: The Journeyman
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for playing at 10 different clubs across 6 countries in Become a Legend.

Achievements.Name: The Super Hero
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for being named World Footballer of the Year in BECOME A LEGEND.

Achievements.Name: Mr. Consistency (Online)
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning 75% of your Last 20 Ranked matches Online.

Achievements.Name: Made the Knockout phase
Achievements.Description: Awarded for making the Knockout phase of the UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: European Champions
Achievements.Description: Awarded when you win the UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: Kings of Latin America
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for winning the Copa Santander Libertadores.
